{"tid":1411160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍女義士事件證明一件事 半夜的確係有一班五毛 呢班五毛係想幫港共同警犬冷處理所有事","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:40:25.000Z","uid":288670,"like":89,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"02a57ae7efb166b47639d51a2228a7ef973b75f8","tid":1411160,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"好似尋晚天水圍女義士事件咁 一大班同正常人思維模式相反  不停叫人唔好將圖share出去 表面上係話唔想女義士受二次傷害 實際就想同件事降溫同等人淡化件事<br />\n<br />\n仲有一大班好似無感情 完全唔識嬲既人仲不停叫其他人冷靜/之後再清算<br />\n<br />\n你話半夜一大班人帶風向叫人勇武？我就話半夜一大班人帶風和等人淡化同冷處理警犬之前做既仆街野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/05/QzE25h.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F05%2FQzE25h.jpeg&h=1c2ed364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/05/9aogXE.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F05%2F9aogXE.jpeg&h=5c2cf3c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/05/ZEqFTG.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F05%2FZEqFTG.jpeg&h=49a6dea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/05/lK4vAU.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F05%2FlK4vAU.jpeg&h=234f76b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bab64aa163a1f8d6289e10a13f3cde1dc0688cc","tid":1411160,"uid":288670,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:06:31.000Z","msg":"今次如果唔係個本人出番黎話唔介意 一定又會俾呢班淡化五毛帶撚晒風向"},{"pid":"001a538ee5c4f10ab3c727543c490a7918268c38","tid":1411160,"uid":288670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:08:59.000Z","msg":"推推先"},{"pid":"a6ff0f00f47799da7156e533783686f403fa2496","tid":1411160,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:09:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c19753a85b62676cbb5ac95cc191c5f0e67964a6","tid":141